title: [Emerald Forest, Blackberry Row]
description: A few exploratory tendrils from the mass of blackberry bushes to the southeast have crept out onto the path, looking for more territory to annex.  Several saplings have gained a toehold here, and already their slender branches spread handfuls of shining leaves as an offering to the sun.
